            <thetext>When selecting an item from the API list panel on the right of qx.Website&#39;s 
Apiviewer, the selected item is moved to the top. This is irritating, makes 
navigation harder and breaks with most other implementations of such navigation 
bars (and hence, user expectations).

If you want to re-position the list at all, a common pattern would be to move 
selected items more to the middle of the view if the item was close enough to 
the upper or lower border when it was selected (making the &quot;surrounding&quot; of the 
item visible).</thetext>
